http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Hyderabad/Buildings-for-1000-gram-panchayats/article13976345.ece

The Telangana government has given permission for construction of buildings to 1,000 gram panchayats in the State.The Panchayat Raj K.T. Rama Rao stated in a release that the government order in this regard would be issued on Friday.The sanction includes buildings for 344 gram panchayats that did not have any accommodation so far and new constructions for 656 gram panchayats whose buildings were in a dilapidated condition. The government decided to permit the buildings on the basis of suggestions received from public during preparation of micro level plans in villages, Mr. Rao said.